Its Your Choice----By Jessica Ross
its your choice to make 
wether you choose to love or wether you choose to hate
you can choose to be nice to your friends and family
but we cant always make the right choices can we?
and thats the great thing about life...
the choices we make
the chances we take 
its our decision
now try to envision
a world all the same
everyday would be sunny,not one drop of rain
it would be so dull and boring
that kind of world my friend i plan NOT to maintain
so wether the choice great or small
make it yours ....give it your all
dont worry wether the choice is smart
just think of your choice as a uniqe piece of art
make people SEE it, and let it be heard
by the power of voice
just SCREAM " Its My Choice!"
but keep in mind its his and hers too
but most important of all, what i tell you is true
its your choice 
so get up
get out
and so WHATEVER the HELL you wanna do!

The Keys to Your Heart

You are attracted to those who are unbridled, untrammeled, and free.
In love, you feel the most alive when your lover is creative and never lets you feel bored.
You'd like to your lover to think you are flexible and ready for anything!
You would be forced to break up with someone who was ruthless, cold-blooded, and sarcastic.
Your ideal relationship is open. Both of you can talk about everything... no secrets.
Your risk of cheating is zero. You care about society and morality. You would never break a commitment.
You think of marriage as something precious. You'll treasure marriage and treat it as sacred.
In this moment, you think of love as something you thirst for. You'll do anything for love, but you won't fall for it easily.
What Are The Keys To Your Heart?
